{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"东方巨龙在腾飞","authors":["张致祥"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":3,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方巨龙在腾飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张致祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋西岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个古老神秘的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有人用战舰筑起路障，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反说什么“铁幕”后面“昏天黑地”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人用谎言编织成藩篱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反说什么“竹幕”后面“扑朔迷离”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实在这里生活的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一群解放了的奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不信天、不信地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只坚信自己才能救自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们曾经挣脱了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝王诸侯的束缚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也治愈了外来的鳞伤遍体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们站起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把世上一切美好的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶进自己的头脑、肌体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接光明的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接和平的新世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这块国土里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融合着古老和现代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀着光辉与神奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出善良、友谊的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎一切朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们只有一个愿望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做新世纪的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再做任何人的奴隶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的巨龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在昂首奋翼腾飞！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}